\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Ah, don't worry. I've taken care of all your
belongings.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Suu~~~h, phew... There's a faint scent of Minato in the
air...
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]S-Stop it, you idiot...

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]The toilet seat that touched Minato's bare butt... I
wonder how much it's worth.
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Th-There's no way it would sell...

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]I bought this for you, but it seems like you
haven't used it much.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Is that so... But, you don't have to apologize or
anything...

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF](Huh? Why are there bite marks on the apple
figurine...)

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Suu~~~h, phew... There's a faint scent of Minato in the
air...
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]S-Stop it, you idiot...
In the quiet room, an old clock ticks away the time.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF](I bet there's a hidden camera in this clock. Though
the angle isn't great for capturing good
images...)
\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Why did I put firewood here again?
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]Don't ask me...
\n<Udo>\F[\V[4]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF](I must say... I have an ugly face, don't I?)

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF](That must be the toilet that someone used. Tsk... I'll
make sure to have those dogs clean it properly.)

\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF](What's inside this... Ah, damn it, I forgot. I'll have
to find an opportunity to make the dogs organize
it...)
\n<Udo>\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF](Half of it has become a storage room, huh...)
SetCharLight -1 5 1 20
